&nbsp;
I In concrete, cantile parks represent the sum of two projects, that is the "Parco" intended as urban and periurban green and the "canile" that, combined together, fulfil a very precise purpose: on the one hand to promote the adoption of dogs and the turn over of animals, on the other hand, to give the possibility to municipalities, singles or associates to recover their green, urban or periurban spaces, usufruibile citizens.
&nbsp;
In addition to ensuring greater comfort for the animals housed, according to the proposal of regional law, and a lower cost in terms of the presence of cement a lower use of water for cleaning, it also wants to guarantee on the one hand a lower risk for the groundwaters standing the crystallization in the surface layers of the soil and, moreover, a greater frequentation by the citizens in order to allow an increase of the possibilities for adoption for the animals that constitutes the primary function. "We want to thank the Councillor for the Budget of the Municipality of Viterbo Elena Angiani for working with us to this innovative text - added Tidei and Nobili - considering the importance of the theme and the numerous requests in this sense that come from the territories of Lazio, we hope that the other political forces can converge on this proposal and that the same can be incardinated quickly in the Commission, and then arrive in room for discussion and final vote".
&nbsp;
The proposal for a law provides that alongside some wall elements and the shelter area that will still have to comply with precise and functional criteria for animal welfare, the Canile Park will have to develop paths of passage with benches, tree-lined areas, lawn spaces with spaces dedicated to children, areas of education where to be able to carry out courses of pet -terapy to be destined outside, courses carried out by professional educators that help the cognitive animal to recover
&nbsp;
The bill consists of three articles: the first article previews an amendment of article 1 of l.r. 34/ 1997 with the preview of the canile parks, which green spaces where it is possible to recreate a habitat that respects the needs of the animal and with the presence of paths open to the public where to promote the correct relationship with the dog and improve the relationship man-dog in order to facilitate its adoption. Article 2, inserts Article 5a, where the purposes of the Canyl Parks are specified and the activities that in it can be carried out, requiring, at the Regional Council, the fixing of the criteria for their realization with reference to the subdivision in categories between puppies, old dogs, adoptable dogs, hardly adoptable dogs, dogs with socialization disorders; to the grassy area useful to create the ambientation of public park, with access routes, benches and areas for people and children; to the type of vegetation useful to the planting that does not apply toxicity to animals, that not guests parasites and that is deprived of horizontal roots able to damage the structure; to the type of box to accommodate dogs, metratures and their characteristics; to the type of reception and assistance services for the dogs hosted including the sanitary one.
&nbsp;
The municipalities, individual or associated, on the basis of the criteria adopted with the deliberation of Giunta, present to the Region special projects in which the characteristics of the canile park are contained and to whose realization can also contribute private resources. Article 3, in the end, amends Article 26 of l.r. 34/1997, in relation to financial forecasting, establishing a specific chapter of expenditure where resources are expected to be equal to 500 thousand euros in capital account for the realization of the barrels and euro 150 thousand in part current for the realization of the activities to be carried out within it.&nbsp;Lazio: pdl to create dog parks for abandoned animals. &nbsp;

